  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>In the furthest reaches of space swim <span class=\"name name-special\">cosmic megafauna</span>, aligning their paths with Travellers, dreaming of possible realities.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>在太空深处游荡的<span class=\"name name-special\">宇宙巨型动物</span>与梦想着无限可能性的旅行者们相遇了。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>在太空最深處悠游著<span class=\"name name-special\">宇宙巨型動物</span>，牠們與旅行者路徑對齊，夢想著可能的現實。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>裡改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
